Description

Double bill featuring vintage adaptations of the adventures of two comic book heroes. ‘The Legend of the Lone Ranger’ (1952) stars Clayton Moore as the titular cowboy crimefighter and Jay Silverheels as his faithful sidekick Tonto. It includes the first four episodes of the 1950s TV series. ‘Zorro’s Black Whip’ (1947) stars Linda Stirling as Barbara Meredith, a crusading journalist who assumes the secret identity of The Black Whip in an attempt to rid the town of corruption. Includes all twelve chapters of the cinema serial.
